  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.8LYPguczQUxUtxHF]{UM5 Ch.6: Armor} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.gzpa55qoOo6qq2qt]{UM5 Ch.6: Shields Descriptions} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.5Omv85vwf9Hu3YHJ]{Tech Level 0}</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">This is a heavy titanium shield with grooves on its bottom, allowing for a firm root into the ground. In addition, a locked slit can open once it has been planted.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">If planted into the ground as a bonus action, the shield remains upright and acts as @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.fzRgOPv3Lml078TL]{three-quarters cover}&nbsp;to anyone behind it (as well as offering its bonus to AC). You must be occupying the same space as the shield to receive this benefit.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Forced Defense Shield </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">250 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">+2 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Disadvantage </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">12 lb. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">0</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
